<view class="contain-area">
  <!-- <ad unit-id="adunit-25006b4270efae7d" ad-type="video" ad-theme="white"></ad> -->
  <van-panel title="➊ 第一步">
    <view class="help-content">
      <view class="help-content-text">打开短视频平台，找到您要去水印的短视频，点击「转发」图标，如下图</view>
      <image mode="scaleToFill" src="cloud://remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669.7265-remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669-1309138375/assets/hlep_1.jpeg"></image>
    </view>
  </van-panel>
  <van-panel title="➋ 第二步">
    <view class="help-content">
      <view class="help-content-text">点击【复制链接】按钮，如下图</view>
      <image mode="aspectFit" src="cloud://remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669.7265-remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669-1309138375/assets/hlep_2.jpeg"></image>
    </view>
  </van-panel>
  <van-panel title="➌ 第三步">
    <view class="help-content">
      <view class="help-content-text">打开小程序，点击【粘贴链接】按钮把内容粘贴到文本框，然后点击【立刻去水印】，如下图</view>
      <image mode="aspectFit" src="cloud://remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669.7265-remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669-1309138375/assets/hlep_3.jpeg"></image>
    </view>
  </van-panel>
  <van-panel title="➍ 第四步">
    <view class="help-content">
      <view class="help-content-text">1.点击【保存视频】，无水印的视频就保存到您的手机相册</view>
      <view>2.点击复制视频链接，可以在电脑上打开下载。如下图</view>
      <image mode="aspectFit" src="cloud://remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669.7265-remove-watermark-1fjg3hq6cdcf669-1309138375/assets/hlep_5.jpeg"></image>
    </view>
  </van-panel>
</view>
